	_GNUSTEP_WM_HIDE_APP protocol suport to the window protocols.
	(hidewindow:): implementation of GSDisplayServer method.
	* Source/x11/XGServerEvent.m (processEvent:): process _GNUSTEP_WM_HIDE_APP
	client message.

