	* Source/win32/WIN32Server.m (-setPartentWindow:forChildWindow:),
	* Source/x11/XGServerWindow.m (-setPartentWindow:forChildWindow:):
	Implement new method.
	* Source/cairo/CairoGState.m (-compositeGState:...): Adjust y
	coordinate of point.

