	Notice: you should now use 'make DESTDIR=/tmp/xxx install' if you
	want to relocate all the installation into /tmp/xxx/
	* GNUmakefile.postamble: Use DESTDIR instead of INSTALL_ROOT_DIR
	everywhere.

